In the eleventh month of the first year of Yuanshou, Jupiter entered the Taiwei constellation and moved retrograde, opposing the Right Law Enforcement star. The divination stated: "Ministers will have worries, law enforcers will be executed, or there will be crimes." In the tenth month of the second year, on the day Wuyin, the Marquis of Gao'an, Dong Xian, was dismissed from his position as Grand Marshal, returned to his residence, and committed suicide.
